00:24:00,560 --> 00:24:01,930
<font color=#FFFF00>Martini dua gelas.</font>

368
00:24:03,100 --> 00:24:04,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa, kau masih ingin lagi.</font>

369
00:24:05,330 --> 00:24:06,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Terima kasih, ya.</font>

370
00:24:07,730 --> 00:24:10,860
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa, sampai orang itu pergi,
