<font color=#FFFF00>Penerjemah .: Writer Ayra :.</font>

400
00:26:02,700 --> 00:26:04,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Jaksa Oh Kwang Ho.</font>

401
00:26:04,330 --> 00:26:07,200
<font color=#FFFF00>- Saya Kim Myung Mi dari MBS.
- Selamat pagi.</font>

402
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:10,460
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya dengar, pelaku sebenarnya pembunuhan
